ditor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6 data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\">Using SSH (Linux\/macOS)<\/h6><ol start=\"1\" data-spread=\"false\"><li><p>Use the below command to connect via SSH:<\/p><\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83bf7f1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"83bf7f1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">ssh -i \/path\/to\/your-key.pem ec2-user@your-instance-public-ip<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-88671f6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"88671f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6 data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\">Using PuTTY (Windows)<\/h6><ol start=\"1\" data-spread=\"false\"><li><p>\ud83d\udcbb Download and install <a>PuTTY<\/a>.<\/p><\/li><li><p>Convert your <code>.pem<\/code> key to a <code>.ppk<\/code> key using PuTTYgen (included with PuTTY).<\/p><\/li><li><p>Open PuTTY and enter your EC2 instance&#8217;s public IP address in the <strong>Host Name<\/strong> field.<\/p><\/li><li><p>Under <strong>Connection<\/strong> &gt; <strong>SSH<\/strong> &gt; <strong>Auth<\/strong>, browse and select your <code>.ppk<\/code> file.<\/p><\/li><li><p>Click <strong>Open<\/strong> to connect.<\/p><\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2d883a2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2d883a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6 data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\">Using Mobaxterm (Windows)<\/h6><ol start=\"1\" data-spread=\"false\"><li><p>\ud83d\udce6 Download and install <a>Mobaxterm<\/a>.<\/p><\/li><li><p>Select <strong>Session<\/strong> &gt; <strong>SSH<\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><li><p>Enter your EC2 instance&#8217;s public IP address.<\/p><\/li><li><p>Provide the username (<code>ec2-user<\/code>) and browse for your <code>.pem<\/code> key under the <strong>Advanced SSH settings<\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><li><p>Click <strong>OK<\/strong> to start the SSH session.<\/p><\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-efd2b55 e-con-full e-flex wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no e-con e-child\" data-id=\"efd2b55\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;full&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f66a4c8 e-flex e-con-boxed wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"f66a4c8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e72b3e7 e-con-full e-flex wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e72b3e7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;full&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2c25127 e-con-full e-flex wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no elementor-invisible e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2c25127\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInRight&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-838f7a9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"838f7a9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" dat